  "text": "Interestingly, adoptive transfer experiments revealed that the CHS response could be elicited when lymph node cells from sensitized wt mice were injected into the ears of STAT6 Ϫ/Ϫ mice. These data indicate that STAT6 is an important signal during the induction phase, as also suggested previously by recent reports [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
